  "review_decision": "The tracked curated reader manuscript renders locally to HTML, EPUB, DOCX, and PDF and passes structural artifact inspection. The DOCX and PDF renders use ten temporary PNG fallbacks generated from the tracked SVG key figures inside the ignored build workspace, and the PDF render now also uses 50 temporary Chrome-screenshot Mermaid fallbacks so browser-rendered diagram labels survive without clipping. The refreshed PDF all-page text/bounding-box audit checked 505 pages, 169762 word boxes, 0 textless pages, 0 out-of-bounds word boxes, 0 layout lines over 160 characters, and required text markers; the all-page raster audit reports 0 blank pages, 0 low-ink pages, and 0 near-edge pages. EPUB, DOCX, and PDF remain unapproved because application-level e-reader/DOCX/PDF review has not happened and no edition release record exists.",
